measure.CatchLine: Establishes Oregon Right to Rest Act.
measure.MeasureSummary:
Establishes Oregon Right to Rest Act. Makes violation unlawful practice enforceable by Commissioner of Bureau of Labor and Industries or by civil action. 
	Takes effect on 91st day following adjournment sine die.
measure.RelatingToFull: Relating to rights of persons experiencing homelessness; creating new provisions; amending ORS 659A.885; and prescribing an effective date.
measure.RelatingTo: Relating to rights of persons experiencing homelessness; prescribing an effective date.
measure.FiscalImpact: May have fiscal impact, but no statement yet issued
measure.RevenueImpact: May have revenue impact, but no statement yet issued

historyActions.ActionText: First reading. Referred to Speaker's desk.
